fields.name: Total last 3 years
fields.formula: sum(filter(lookup('Performance rewiews','Overall performance rating'),lookup('Performance rewiews','Year') > (field('Last review') - 3)))

fields.name: Average last 3 years
fields.formula: if(field('Count reviews') = 0,0,sum(filter(lookup('Performance rewiews','Overall performance rating'),lookup('Performance rewiews','Year') > (field('Last review') - 3))) / count(filter(lookup('Performance rewiews','Overall performance rating'),lookup('Performance rewiews','Year') > (field('Last review') - 3))))

fields.name: Sustained performance
fields.formula: if(field('Average last 3 years') = 0,'N/A',if(field('Average last 3 years') < 2.5,'Low',if(field('Average last 3 years') < 3.5,'Medium','High')))

fields.name: Has potential
fields.formula: every(filter(lookup('Potential assessments','Has potential'),lookup('Potential assessments','Year') = field('Last review')))

fields.name: Has ability
fields.formula: every(filter(lookup('Ability assessments','Has ability'),lookup('Ability assessments','Year') = field('Last review')))

fields.name: Category
fields.formula: if(field('Sustained performance') = 'N/A','Too Soon to Rate',if(field('Sustained performance') = 'Low','Improve',if(field('Has ability'),'Accelerate','Grow')))

fields.name: Needs review link
fields.formula: if(field('Needs review'),concat('+ Add performance review for ',field('Next review')),'')

fields.name: Needs potential assessment
fields.formula: and(count(filter(field('Potential assessments'),lookup('Potential assessments','Year') = field('Last review'))) = 0,field('Meets potential requirements'))

fields.name: Needs potential assessment link
fields.formula: if(field('Needs potential assessment'),concat('+ Add potential assessment for ',field('Last review')),'')

fields.name: Needs ability assessment
fields.formula: and(count(filter(field('Ability assessments'),lookup('Ability assessments','Year') = field('Last review'))) = 0,field('Meets ability requirements'))

fields.name: Needs ability assessment link
fields.formula: if(field('Needs ability assessment'),concat('+ Add ability assessment for ',field('Last review')),'')

fields.name: Needs accelerated assessment
fields.formula: and(count(filter(field('Accelerated assessments'),lookup('Accelerated assessments','Year') = field('Last review'))) = 0,field('Meets accelerated requirements'))

fields.name: Needs accelerated assessment link
fields.formula: if(field('Needs accelerated assessment'),concat('+ Add accelerated assessment for ',field('Last review')),'')
